data.Name: FKJ
data.Bio: Futuristically Classy, Vincent Fenton, French Kiwi Juice. Better known by the abbreviation FKJ, has mastered the sound of sophisticatedly, smooth electronic music. With serene sounds perfect for posh settings, FKJ with his strong catalogue of tracks has found himself on repeat in the dwellings of all Roche Musique alumni. Lying together his first track to hit the charts is built off of a mellow, heartfelt sample, and leyered with classic electronic keyboards, and a beautiful guitar bass. Read more on Last.fm
